lead_paragraph: Chelsea's former doctor Eva Carneiro, who left after a public spat with team manager Jose Mourinho, rejected a 1.2 million pound ($1.7 million) settlement from the London club, British media reported, citing employment tribunal papers.

headline.print_headline: Ex-Chelsea Doctor Refuses Payout From Club in Dismissal Case-Reports
